cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this software in academic work or in a public report,
  please cite it using the metadata in this file.
title: site-context-pipeline
abstract: >-
  Offline-first command-line toolkit for building structured site
  context packs for human-reviewed, LLM-assisted content workflows.
  Reads URL inventories, internal link graphs, keyword data, and
  search performance signals from local files and emits a
  deterministic JSON + Markdown digest reproducible from a single
  workspace directory.
